data.title: Youth week stand up comedy workshop with Anthony Lamond
data.meta_description: Calling all teens aged 13-18. Join stand up comedian and comedy producer Anthony Lamond for a three-hour workshop on the art of Stand Up Comedy for a special Youth Week 2023 event.
data.text:
Calling all teens aged 13-18. Join stand up comedian and comedy show producer Anthony Lamond for a three-hour workshop on the art of stand up comedy at this special Youth Week 2023 event.

What will I learn?

The science of laughter

Developing a character for the stage

Sourcing material and writing for yourself

Stage craft

Microphone technique

Shaping, editing and finalising your material

Producing your own show and building your own audience

Develop a 2-5 minute comedy routine for your graduation performance

Australian comedian and actor Anthony Lamond is a producer of comedy shows and has shared the stage with high profile comedians such as Dave Hughes, Jimeoin, Arj Barker,Fiona O'Loughlin, Peter Rowsthorn, Cal Wilson, Merrick Watts, Lawrence Mooney, The Old Fella, Chris Franklin, Heath Franklin and Bob Franklin just to name a few.

Lunch will be provided.
